{"abstract":[{"text":"Run scripts automatically when a VM boots.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Provisioning","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode","level":3,"text":"Choosing a Mode","type":"heading"},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Mode","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Status","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Works without setup?","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Network needed?","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Best for","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","type":"reference"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Working"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need SSH enabled"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Cloned VMs with SSH","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In progress"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Need agent installed","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OCI images (future)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","type":"reference","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need watcher"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No-disk-modify environments"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"SSH-Working","text":"SSH (Working)"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress","text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"bash","type":"codeListing","code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned","text":"Guest Agent (Planned)"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned","text":"Shared Folder (Planned)"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mode is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"article","sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"Provisioning Virtual Machines","roleHeading":"API Collection","role":"collectionGr